      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without the high price tag of a newer model. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car would benefit from a routine service and potentially new tires in the near future. Cosmetically, there are visible scuffs on the bumpers and some interior wear consistent with its age and mileage. All major systems like the heater and lights work, but please expect some minor quirks typical of a well-used vehicle. It is being sold as-is, offering a solid foundation for anyone willing to put in a little bit of TLC.",
