    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver a linear 333 hp, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014addressing the critical preventative maintenance required for this chassis. The suspension geometry is sharpened by refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the communicative steering and neutral handling balance the M-division is known for. With the M Variable Differential Lock providing optimal traction out of corners, this example is ready for spirited driving. Finished in Carbon Black with a well-preserved Nappa leather interior, it strikes the perfect balance between a preserved classic and a high-performance driver\u2019s tool.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
