      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, impressive luster, though a discerning eye will notice minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014imperfections consistent with careful, regular use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is supple with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. All interior technology, including the navigation system and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It features a comprehensive service history with a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of tires installed within the last year. The engine runs quietly, the gear transitions are seamless, and the handling remains sharp and predictable. This is a solid, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
